1.0.name: wordpress/blogolife
1.0.description: BlogoLife is a simple and perfect HTML5&CSS3 theme for personal blogging that supports post formats, and several customization options. The custom background, custom header, and multiple color schemes gives you the possibility to adapt your blog as you wish.
